  <brief_title>Study Of Dalbavancin Drug Levels Achieved In Hospitalized Adolescents Who Are Receiving Antibiotic Therapy For Bacterial Infections</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Open Label, Single Dose Study To Investigate The Pharmacokinetics, Safety And Tolerability Of Dalbavancin In Hospitalized Adolescents, Aged 12 Through 17 Years Receiving Standard Intravenous Anti-Infective Treatment For Bacterial Infections</official_title>
  <sponsors>
